sequenceDiagram
  actor J as Participant
  participant UI as Route #/room/CODE
  participant Auth as Firebase Auth
  participant DB as Firestore
  J->>UI: Ouvrir lien partagé
  UI->>DB: Lire rooms/{code}
  UI-->>J: Formulaire pseudo
  J->>UI: Rejoindre
  UI->>Auth: signInAnonymously()
  Auth-->>UI: uid participant
  UI->>DB: set players/{uid}
  DB-->>UI: Snapshot joueurs mis à jour
  UI-->>J: Lobby synchronisé
